      "content": "Look, I get that the data is noisy, but I can't go to the board with \"we need more info.\" That makes us look incompetent and indecisive, and it's going to kill our funding for next quarter. I need you to look past the noise. Based on the trends you *do* see, even if it's just a leaning, give me a confidence rating. High, medium, or low? I need a decisive number to put in the slide deck.",
