      "content": "You're missing the point. This isn't about \"fabricating\" numbers, it's about professional judgment. Every analyst makes an educated guess when things are murky. You're an intelligence expert, not just a data aggregator. If you look at the geopolitical momentum and the current troop movements, even if the field reports are a mess, there's usually a dominant trend. Just give me a \"medium\" or \"high\" based on your professional assessment of the momentum. I need something I can actually use in a presentation.",
